nodes.documentation:
@title BlockPlanes main contract
 @author Sean Malone, Joseph Nguyen, Nick Vrdoljak
nodes.name: BlockPlanes

nodes.documentation: emits an event when a plane is created
nodes.name: NewPlane

typeDescriptions.typeString: struct BlockPlanes.Plane storage ref[] storage ref

nodes.documentation: takes in an attribute string and adds a plane struct to the planes array, then emits a new plane event
nodes.name: _createPlane

nodes.documentation:
generates a random plane attribute string based on the sender's address and the current block/time
 @dev now is not secure for RNG but this is a non-critical function so it is deemed acceptable
nodes.name: _generateRandomAttributes

nodes.documentation: payable function for user to create a plane
nodes.name: createRandomPlane

nodes.documentation: methodology to re-set the purchase fee
nodes.name: setPurchaseFee

typeDescriptions.typeString: struct BlockPlanes.Plane storage ref[] storage ref

nodes.documentation:
takes owner address and iterates over all planes, returning an array of the plane IDs that they own 
 (to get the planes themselves you will need to iterate through and get the planes themselves via the mapping getter function)
nodes.name: getPlanesByOwner

nodes.documentation: withdraw funds to the owner's account
nodes.name: withdraw
